     <li> <a href=jxhelp:CBEditorHelp#SourceCode>Labels menu</a>
     <li> Included in <a href=jxhelp:CBSymbolHelp>symbol browser</a>
     <li> Included in <a href=jxhelp:CBProjectHelp>Make.files</a>
     <li> Compilable via the Project menu
     </ul>
